title: Match History page online doesn't load
body: Tried to load Match History both from the LoL website and by going in client and clicking to view on web.  Tried to see in both Firefox and IE but I just get a background with an empty white box where the info should be.

replies.body:
Damn, I know this can be pretty flipping annoying. This is actually a known bug with the match history webpage. If you'd like, you can report this on our [**Bug Tracker**](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report) so it can be better tracked.

Let me know if you have any questions.
